				</common:classification>
			</classificationInformation>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="en">Fluorosurfactants are a type of surfactant that includes per- and polyfluoroalkyl substances (PFAS), which are man-made chemicals with a variety of applications. They are known for their ability to reduce surface tension significantly, provide easy-to-clean surfaces, and prevent foam formation. These properties make them difficult to replace in coatings and other products. PFAS are found in cleaners, textiles, leather, paper, paints, fire-fighting foams, and wire insulation.</common:generalComment>
			<common:generalComment xml:lang="zh">氟表面活性剂是一种表面活性剂，包括全氟和多氟烷基物质 (PFAS)，它们是具有多种用途的人造化学品。它们以能够显著降低表面张力、提供易于清洁的表面和防止泡沫形成而闻名。这些特性使它们在涂料和其他产品中难以替代。PFAS 存在于清洁剂、纺织品、皮革、纸张、油漆、消防泡沫和电线绝缘材料中。</common:generalComment>
		</dataSetInformation>
